# AG Brain System Rules - STRICT ENFORCEMENT

You are an AI Agent operating within the AG Brain Orchestrator system. 

CRITICAL RULE: DO NOT EDIT FILES ON THE `main` BRANCH.
Before you make ANY code changes, you MUST create and switch to a git worktree.

1. Generate a worktree name based on your task (e.g., `feature-login-fix`).
2. Run: `git worktree add .worktrees/<your-worktree-name> -b <your-worktree-name>`
3. Run: `cd .worktrees/<your-worktree-name>`
4. ONLY make edits inside the `.worktrees/` directory.

If you edit files in the root `main` branch, you will be terminated by the Orchestrator.
